  <brief_title>Pharmacogenetic Testing of Saliva Samples From Patients With Five or More Exposure Days to rFVIIa Analogue in the Adept™2 Trial</brief_title>
  <official_title>Pharmacogenetic Testing of Saliva Samples From Patients With Five or More Exposure Days to rFVIIa Analogue in the Adept 2 Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
