  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is conducted globally. This study describes pharmacogenetic testing of saliva
      samples from patients who participated in the NN1731-3562 trial (adept™2) (NCT01392547). The
      objective is to determine the HLA (human leukocyte antigen) type and polymorphisms in the
      FVII gene in patients previously exposed to rFVIIa analogue.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
